descriptionHtml:
Download TOTUM now to access a world of big-brand savings!
With TOTUM you’ll SAVE-BIG on your everyday shopping, eat & drink out for less, get discounted travel, make savings at 100,000s of locations all over the world - and much, much more!

SAVE OVER £550 A YEAR ON YOUR EVERYDAY SHOPPING with 600+ discounts at 400+ big brands like Apple, Samsung, Adidas, Asos and Sky across tech and mobile, travel, fashion, beauty, food and drink, health & fitness and more!
REDUCE YOUR ANNUAL SUPERMARKET BILLS BY £100s and earn up to 14% cashback on your everyday purchases both in-store and online at over 80 big-name brands including Sainsbury’s, Asda, Boots, Primark, Ikea and M&S with the TOTUM Cashback VISA card.

SAVE 25% ON TAKEAWAY COFFEE AND DINING OUT with FREE tastecard and Coffee Club (RRP up to £74.98 a year). TOTUM+ members can save up to £234 a year on dining out, takeaway coffee, pizza delivery, enjoying the latest movie releases and even epic days out!
FREE GOVERNMENT-APPROVED PROOF-OF-AGE ID. Going on a night out? Leave your passport at home with TOTUM ID! Supported by the Home Office, the Chartered Trading Standards Institute and the National Police Chiefs' Council, TOTUM ID comes in two versions - one for 18+ and one for 16-17 year olds.
100,000S OF DISCOUNTS IN OVER 90 COUNTRIES WORLDWIDE. If you’re a student, a teacher or you’re aged 35 and under, the International Student Identity Card (ISIC), International Youth Travel Card (IYTC) or International Teacher Identity Card (ITIC) are your key to unlocking an amazing range of savings all over the world.

NOT JUST FOR STUDENTS - Although we’re big on student discounts, you don’t have to be a student to join TOTUM - From apprentices, to professional learners, to trade union members and more, visit totum.com/eligibility to see if you can join and make your money go further!
